, the observed correlation between\n$\\Delta K_{0}$ and $L_{K}$ can be considered as a direct evidence for AGN\nfeedback in galaxy groups and clusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Jun 2010 06:38:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-19"}
